    <scopecontent>
      <head>Scope and Content
</head>
      <p>Records, 1686-1875, of Middlesex County Circuit Court consist of a copy of an inventory and appraisement of Roger Jones' estate (1741), copy of the appraisement of Ralph and John Wormley's estate (1830), copy
of Eleanor Wormley's will (1815), and extracts from deed books, will books, marriage records, inventories, and appraisements (1686-1825) that were copied by an unidentified individual in 1875.
</p>
    </scopecontent>
